      <hedline>
        <hl1>And Plenty of Ice</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Frank Folis letter on Alex Witchel's June 14 article on ordering tap water in restaurant</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>When a waiter asks us about our choice of water (''Water Pressure: Never Higher,'' June 14), we have a standard reply: Aqua Giuliani. It works every time.</p>
        <p>FRANK FOLIS  Brooklyn</p>
      </block>
